{"title":"深圳河畔","authors":["陈残云"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":4,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳河畔（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈残云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳河畔的彼岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个年轻的英国兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常寂寞地歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那声调是悲伤的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在思念迢迢万里的亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和久别的田庄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时候，他的枪杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂上酒瓶、女人的袜子；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显然，他学会了颓唐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"显然，他是个庄稼汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对枪杆没有兴趣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但不容许他自由挑选。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他日盼夜盼归故乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愿意钉在别人的国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但不容他自由挑选！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那末，小伙子呵，你唱吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的歌声并不孤单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地中海上同样有你的同伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳河畔的彼岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜夜都有探照灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们村庄上守夜的民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都懂得，这灯光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是神经衰弱的象征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳河畔的彼岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七年如一日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经常都有作战式的炮声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们村庄上的种田人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都懂得，这炮声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是神经衰弱的象征！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是呀，我们一切人都懂得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在灯光与炮声的后面有阴影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有罪恶的政治亡魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行着黑暗的买卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝望的破坏和暗算！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}